OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1784051302
OL,3,CMore than 2,000 dog attacks on Royal
OL,4,CMail staff in past year
OL,6,FOne Bristol postal worker has
OL,7,Fdescribed her horror at getting bitten
OL,8,Fby a dog as Royal Mail says there have
OL,9,Fbeen more than 2,000 dog attacks on
OL,10,Fits staff in the past year.
OL,12,FWhile this is a decrease, the company
OL,13,Fsays it's unacceptably high.
OL,15,FKaty Davies was badly bitten on her
OL,16,Fround in Bristol in January and says
OL,17,Fit's left her a shell of her former
OL,18,Fself.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
