OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1784051302
OL,3,CMore than 2,000 dog attacks on Royal
OL,4,CMail staff in past year
OL,6,FShe says she had never had any
OL,7,Fincidents with dogs before the ordeal
OL,8,Fand there had not been "any signs"
OL,9,Fsomething like this could happen to
OL,10,Fher.
OL,12,F"As I turned the corner, I saw
OL,13,Fsomething out of the corner of my eye.
OL,14,FIt was very quick and very large, and
OL,15,Fbefore I knew it, I felt extreme
OL,16,Fimpact and pain in my lower right leg,
OL,17,Fand I was on the floor screaming.
OL,19,F"It felt like I had been hit by a mini
OL,20,Fbus."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1784051302
OL,3,CMore than 2,000 dog attacks on Royal
OL,4,CMail staff in past year
OL,6,FShe says she was "lucky" the dog
OL,7,Flatched onto her, but she was still
OL,8,Fleft with five "incredibly painful"
OL,9,Fpuncture bites.
OL,11,F"The damage left from even a clean
OL,12,Fbite was immense. I didn't know how
OL,13,Fmuch worse it was going to get - both
OL,14,Fphysically and mentally".
OL,16,FMs Davies decides feeling even more
OL,17,Fscared when she learned from the
OL,18,Fdoctors that her wound wasn't healing
OL,19,Fwell at first.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1784051302
OL,3,CMore than 2,000 dog attacks on Royal
OL,4,CMail staff in past year
OL,6,F"My anxiety and depression really
OL,7,Fkicked in," she says, adding that it
OL,8,Ftook three months to get back to a
OL,9,Fgood range of mobility.
OL,11,FShe stills feels "not quite there"
OL,12,Feven six months after as one of the
OL,13,Fbites was close to a tendon.
OL,15,F"I'm going to have to life with this
OL,16,Ftendon damage, and my mobility around
OL,17,Fit, forever."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1784051302
OL,3,CMore than 2,000 dog attacks on Royal
OL,4,CMail staff in past year
OL,6,FMs Davies says she never expected the
OL,7,Fmental strain that would come from it,
OL,8,Fand she became a "shell of (her)
OL,9,Fformer self" following the attack.
OL,11,FMeanwhile, Bristol City Council
OL,12,Fcandidate Danica Priest has told of
OL,13,Fher horror after she had part of her
OL,14,Ffinger bitten off for a dog while
OL,15,Fdelivering campaign leaflets during
OL,16,Fthe local election.
OL,18,F"I put one of my leaflets through the
OL,19,Fdoor and I took my hand out and saw
OL,20,Fblood, and knew something was wrong
OL,21,Fand I went into shock".
OL,26,@pD@\pmpD@`pn
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1784051302
OL,3,CMore than 2,000 dog attacks on Royal
OL,4,CMail staff in past year
OL,6,FShe called 999 after realising part of
OL,7,Fher finger had been bitten off.
OL,9,F"I'd never had any issues before".
OL,11,FThe dog had no known history of
OL,12,Fviolence or biting anyone, Ms Priest
OL,13,Fadded.
OL,15,FThe local campaigner had to have
OL,16,Freconstructive surgery on her finger
OL,17,Fand remove part of the bone.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
