OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1784051302
OL,3,CMore than 2,000 dog attacks on Royal
OL,4,CMail staff in past year
OL,6,FLizz Lloyd, Group Director for Health
OL,7,Fand Safety at the Royal Mail, says the
OL,8,Fcompany have seen "horrendous attacks"
OL,9,Fover the years, including facial
OL,10,Finjuries.
OL,12,F"All of this is preventable if we work
OL,13,Ftogether," she says, recommending
OL,14,Fowners consider dog gates.
OL,16,F"It's about thinking about your
OL,17,Fanimal's triggers and how you can help
OL,18,Fit".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
